description:
Bridget Faye is a member of the http://anidb.net/ch32498 [Black Order] and the Assistant Branch Head of the http://anidb.net/ch32499 [European Branch], under Branch Head and Chief Officer http://anidb.net/ch83366 [Komui Lee]. A former secretary from http://anidb.net/ch32502 [Central], she was transferred to the European Branch after it was moved to its new location and expanded with other Central personnel.
Source: D.Gray-man Wiki
name: Bridget Faye
